        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19050044/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19050044/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/byrd/" class=" " title="尘埃">尘埃</a>
                (人生无常 活在当下~~)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="19050044">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">挖个坑，继续读，这是今年读书计划里的一本。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-06-18 13:38</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                挖个坑，继续读，这是今年读书计划里的一本。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
