            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="35404189">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4157677/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4157677-3.jpg" alt="加盐的雪碧" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35404189/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35404189/" class="">第9页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4157677/" class=" " title="加盐的雪碧">加盐的雪碧</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="35404189">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">记下</span>
